categories.title: Recent Pull Requests in elizaOS/eliza Repository

content.text: Several pull requests have been completed in the elizaOS/eliza repository. Bug fixes include PR #4496 which addressed issues with the TTS manager and transcribe functionality, and PR #4510 which fixed a problem with deleting agents that have been in a room. Other improvements include PR #4508 which enhanced message handling and text escaping by adding null checks. Documentation was updated with PR #4483 modifying the README.md file and PR #4488 creating a new README_IND.md file. Additionally, PR #4501 was merged for the 0.25.19 release.
